WEBVTT

00:00.674 --> 00:01.504
Give us a shout
when you're in.

00:01.575 --> 00:02.803
Okay... okay!

00:07.748 --> 00:08.908
Not worth getting
out of bed for.

00:08.982 --> 00:11.712
Go away! A tenner for two hours
work's not bad, is it?

00:11.785 --> 00:13.753
We'll be back home before
the kids go to school.

00:13.821 --> 00:15.288
Why can't we get involved
in laying it?

00:15.355 --> 00:16.822
We'd make a few more bob
out of that.

00:17.591 --> 00:19.684
He's got another gang there
doing it, that's why.

00:19.760 --> 00:21.250
He's got a couple of gangs working
for him then, has he?

00:21.328 --> 00:22.022
Got loads fellas working
for him.

00:22.096 --> 00:24.121
He has one gang cutting it,
one gang laying it.

00:24.198 --> 00:25.825
But he's got gangs all over
the bloody country.

00:25.899 --> 00:27.696
Does loads of work, you know,
Dixie.

00:27.768 --> 00:30.236
You'd think he'd have a decent
van... Jesus Christ!

00:30.304 --> 00:34.638
What does he want a decent
van for, for bloody old soil and
wheelbarrows and spades!

00:34.708 --> 00:40.044
That's pushed my piles back
about a fortnight.

